  - Mage
  - Girl
  - Girl
  dialogueLines:
  - Oh, great. A book.
  - (opens it)
  - "\u2026Empty?"
  - '(flipping pages) '
  - "There\u2019s only one line here: \"Words appear where there is a catalyst.\""
  - Was that a hint or a threat?
  - An instruction manual.
  - Do you ever have normal ones?
  - "No. They don\u2019t survive."
  - "There\u2019s a recipe here\u2026"
  - Of course.
  - "You didn\u2019t think answers would come for free, did you?"
  - I was hoping.
  - Bad habit.
  dialogueManager: {fileID: 1137868402286140931}
  playOnlyOnce: 1
  destroyAfterDialogue: 1
